lines.text: The key to winning is knowing all your opponent's weaknesses.
It won't be after tonight. I think it is a great night for a moondance.
Did you notice, there's blood on the moon tonight?
You don't have the killer instinct, I can show it to you.

[to a fellow police officer]
Did you see the Chief? The way he looked. Those big eyes just...
He's right behind me isn't he?
It's a wonderful night for a moon dance.
Noone's gonna mess with me babe, you're just being stupid.
I'm telling you I heard something damnit.
Get back here you dumb bitch!
I have the worst luck with men.
Your luck is about to change.
We have ten minutes for the Grand Championship match! Life? Or death? It's in your hands!
